{"tid":788230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞宣佈解除與中國的基建合約","createTime":"2018-08-21T10:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T15:20:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0e32afc902a72c4cf0ee0adf4cdf157f46f596e9","tid":788230,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞宣佈解除與中國簽訂總額逾二百億美元的基建合約。 <br />\n<br />\n正在北京訪問的馬哈蒂爾表示，大馬會即日起解除前政府和中國簽訂興建配合一帶一路工程的鐵路和一條天然氣管道的合約，直至大馬財政有能力，才重新開始工程。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬哈蒂爾指，他是在訪華期間向中國提出解除基建合約的要求，得到中方體諒，形容中國政府亦不希望大馬變成「破產國家」，馬哈蒂爾昨天分別與國家主席習近平及總理李克強見面，表示希望中方理解目前大馬困境，協助大馬處理國內財政問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/533149/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F533149%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584&d=87bkXItMRM2fHHB6Ip%2FugNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1dd7f314\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F533149%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584&h=8522f0f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/533149/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84</a>"},{"pid":"47e2e43f3565960ca2d5c01d0a0a8c8d2401e